orts healing. It is an approach that is considered reliable and valid in its own tradition. This is in contradistinction to the objective approach of modern science and medicine. This work investigates and contrasts these two approaches to knowledge. An integrated system using both could offer much for disease prevention, health promotion and healing.\nDr Donn Brennan MB BCh BAO, MRCGP, MScAyu, is a general practitioner and is the founding president of the Ayurveda Practitioners Association in the UK. He has authored a book and CDs and he lectures and consults on Ayurveda in Ireland and the UK. He lives in Dublin with his wife Ann.\nEs gelten unsere Allgemeinen Gesch\u00e4ftsbedingungen: www.buecher.de/agb\nImpressum\nwww.buecher.de ist ein Shop der buecher.de GmbH & Co. KG B\u00fcrgermeister-Wegele-Str. 12, 86167 Augsburg Amtsgericht Augsburg HRA 13309", "language": null, "image": "https://bilder.buecher.de/produkte/35/35700/35700107n.jpg", "pagetype": "product", "links": ["https://www.buecher.de/ni/service_topics/answers/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/id/0305/", "https://www.buecher.de/ni/service_topics/answers/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/id/13/", "https://www.buecher.de/ni/service_topics/answers/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/id/020301/", "https://www.buecher.de/go/my_my/my_orders/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/", "https://www.buecher.de/go/my_my/my_login/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/", "https://www.buecher.de/go/my_my/my_logout/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/", "https://www.buecher.de/go/my_wish/overview/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/", "https://www.buecher.de/go/payback/start/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/", null, "https://www.buecher.de/go/home/page/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/", "https://www.buecher.de/go/my_my/my_login/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/", null, "https://www.buecher.de/go/my_wish/overview/session/2nurm9itmph5bcskbeu5kmtgvv/", "https://www.buecher.de/go/cart_cart/cart_show/session/2nurm9itmph5bcsk